1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000 line:0
<b><c.color9CD5FF>One Pace Premium</c></b>
Keep the project alive: <c.colora8c7fa>ko-fi.com/not6ip</c>

2
00:01:30.450 --> 00:01:32.660
Several Hours Ago...

3
00:01:38.870 --> 00:01:41.750
The problem is, the World Government...

4
00:01:44.380 --> 00:01:47.710
doesn't just want to get rid
of Stella, but me, too!

5
00:01:47.750 --> 00:01:53.680
Emperor Red Hair's Pirate Crew

6
00:01:48.210 --> 00:01:50.760
I can't believe them! This sucks!

7
00:01:50.760 --> 00:01:52.220
They'll pay for this, right?!

8
00:01:52.220 --> 00:01:53.680
Well, say something!

9
00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.430
Yes, they'll pay for this.

10
00:01:55.430 --> 00:01:56.390
Too slow!

11
00:01:56.890 --> 00:01:59.390
But if that's what they're up to, I have a plan!

12
00:02:00.220 --> 00:02:01.810
So...

13
00:02:01.810 --> 00:02:06.560
First things first, I need you guys
to take care of all these pests!

14
00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:08.820
I locked down the Frontier Dome,

15
00:02:08.820 --> 00:02:13.780
so kill everyone other than me, Stella,
and the hostages underground!

16
00:02:13.780 --> 00:02:13.860
so kill everyone other than me, Stella,
and the hostages underground!

17
00:02:13.860 --> 00:02:13.950
so kill everyone other than me, Stella,
and the hostages underground!

18
00:02:13.950 --> 00:02:14.030
so kill everyone other than me, Stella,
and the hostages underground!

19
00:02:14.030 --> 00:02:14.110
so kill everyone other than me, Stella,
and the hostages underground!

20
00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:15.740
Understood!

21
00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:18.990
And while you're running amok,

22
00:02:18.990 --> 00:02:22.830
they'll start to wonder who ordered you.

23
00:02:22.830 --> 00:02:23.920
If I'm busted...

24
00:02:24.620 --> 00:02:28.290
there's no way I'll be able to stand up to them!

25
00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:30.340
S-Snake!

26
00:02:30.340 --> 00:02:31.260
Yes, ma'am.

27
00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:34.880
I need you to put on a show
and pretend you got me.

28
00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:35.590
Yes, ma'am.

29
00:02:35.590 --> 00:02:38.180
And make sure to undo it
when no one's looking!

30
00:02:38.180 --> 00:02:38.970
Yes, ma'am!

31
00:02:40.310 --> 00:02:45.190
Also, there's one part of
the lab you need to leave alone.

32
00:02:46.310 --> 00:02:47.690
This goes for all of you.

33
00:02:48.440 --> 00:02:51.280
So listen carefully...

34
00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:53.110
Let the hunt...

35
00:02:53.780 --> 00:02:54.900
begin!

36
00:03:16.340 --> 00:03:18.470
Hurry up! Everyone, get on the ship!

37
00:03:18.850 --> 00:03:21.350
We've got to get off of Egghead!

38
00:03:41.580 --> 00:03:43.330
The Land of War, Elbaph
New World

39
00:03:43.490 --> 00:03:43.790
The Land of War, Elbaph
New World

40
00:03:47.830 --> 00:03:49.460
Are you punks...

41
00:03:50.210 --> 00:03:51.460
ready to rock?

42
00:03:51.460 --> 00:03:53.670
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

43
00:03:54.130 --> 00:03:57.510
Listen up, Kid Pirates!

44
00:03:57.880 --> 00:04:02.050
Our chief is Red-Haired Shanks, you know...

45
00:04:03.060 --> 00:04:05.560
You've got no ribbit to see– I-I mean...

46
00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:07.140
He misspoke!

47
00:04:08.270 --> 00:04:10.190
...you've got no right to see him!

48
00:04:10.190 --> 00:04:11.400
Captain "Frog-Toes" Gerotini
Puddle Pirates

49
00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:15.190
He'f wight!

50
00:04:16.150 --> 00:04:17.530
Pops, your dentures!

51
00:04:17.530 --> 00:04:18.740
Bandmaster Fuga "the Addenturer"
Social Club

52
00:04:18.740 --> 00:04:20.490
Yeah! Dummies!

53
00:04:20.820 --> 00:04:21.910
I hate you!

54
00:04:21.910 --> 00:04:24.160
I will...

55
00:04:25.330 --> 00:04:28.370
never ever...

56
00:04:28.370 --> 00:04:29.710
let you see Chiefy!

57
00:04:29.710 --> 00:04:31.630
You're so brave, Princess!

58
00:04:31.630 --> 00:04:32.840
Pururu "the Brr-rave"
Bourgeois Pirates

59
00:04:34.710 --> 00:04:35.670
Is this a joke?!

60
00:04:35.670 --> 00:04:38.260
I toad you to leave!

61
00:04:36.590 --> 00:04:38.930
These are Red Hair's allies?!

62
00:04:38.260 --> 00:04:41.550
I'll never lose to you!

63
00:04:38.930 --> 00:04:41.550
I thought we were in the New World!

64
00:04:41.550 --> 00:04:45.720
I get what you're saying,
but there are some big names here, too.

65
00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:47.350
Don't let your guard down.

66
00:04:47.350 --> 00:04:51.190
I won't hold back even if
they're nobodies, but...

67
00:04:57.610 --> 00:04:59.450
We're gonna set sail soon!

68
00:04:59.450 --> 00:05:00.320
Chief!

69
00:05:00.820 --> 00:05:03.070
They went to stop the Kid Pirates!

70
00:05:03.070 --> 00:05:04.530
Tell them to pull back!

71
00:05:04.530 --> 00:05:06.620
Before they get hurt!

72
00:05:06.620 --> 00:05:08.160
– Whoa, whoa, whoa!
– Whoa, whoa, whoa!

73
00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:09.910
– Wait, wait, wait!
– Wait, wait, wait!

74
00:05:13.330 --> 00:05:15.590
– What are you talking about, Chief?!
– What are you talking about, Chief?!

75
00:05:15.590 --> 00:05:17.840
I... What are you guys doing?!

76
00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:21.010
I won't let them lay a finger on you!

77
00:05:21.010 --> 00:05:22.050
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

78
00:05:23.300 --> 00:05:26.060
Well, I really appreciate the offer!

79
00:05:26.810 --> 00:05:28.560
But stay away from the sea.

80
00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:30.940
Hey, get off me already!

81
00:05:37.570 --> 00:05:38.990
Don't go!

82
00:05:38.990 --> 00:05:41.150
Let us fight, too!

83
00:05:46.450 --> 00:05:48.290
Come on, guys...

84
00:05:48.660 --> 00:05:49.660
Say it ain't so!

85
00:05:49.660 --> 00:05:51.540
Chief, you leavin' already?

86
00:05:51.540 --> 00:05:53.210
Yeah, Chief!

87
00:05:53.210 --> 00:05:55.170
We only just got to see you!

88
00:05:55.170 --> 00:05:56.540
Sorry about that.

89
00:05:56.540 --> 00:05:58.960
We only swung by on
our way to somewhere else.

90
00:05:59.920 --> 00:06:02.170
Now come on, let go.

91
00:06:03.890 --> 00:06:07.350
We stayed so long, a big shot found us.

92
00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:09.430
Oh, and like I said...

93
00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:11.230
tell the ships to pull back!

94
00:06:11.230 --> 00:06:14.650
Our allies are famously weak after all.

95
00:06:17.570 --> 00:06:19.730
Weak, huh?! You cheeky bastard!

96
00:06:19.730 --> 00:06:22.030
We're still alive thanks to you!

97
00:06:22.030 --> 00:06:24.240
Your flag is what protects us!

98
00:06:24.700 --> 00:06:25.570
Yeah!

99
00:06:25.570 --> 00:06:28.660
Worry less about fighting
and more about aging, Granny Oli.

100
00:06:29.290 --> 00:06:32.540
Oh, put a sock in it, Chief!

101
00:06:32.540 --> 00:06:35.040
You're as popular as ever, Chief!

102
00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:36.540
Oh, please...

103
00:06:36.540 --> 00:06:39.630
Don't worry, Chief. We'll take care of him.

104
00:06:39.630 --> 00:06:42.590
Hey now, he's worth three billion.

105
00:06:43.090 --> 00:06:46.090
Don't underestimate how fast kids grow up.

106
00:06:48.760 --> 00:06:52.850
But have their wounds
from Wano healed already?

107
00:06:52.850 --> 00:06:53.640
Yeah.

108
00:06:54.520 --> 00:06:56.150
They look fine to me.

109
00:06:56.150 --> 00:06:58.270
They're all ready for a scrap.

110
00:06:58.270 --> 00:06:59.520
That's good...

111
00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:02.820
Any updates on Blackbeard?

112
00:07:03.150 --> 00:07:06.780
Nah, just that he definitely
left the Pirate Island.

113
00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:09.740
I thought for sure he'd show up in Wano.

114
00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.040
Hongo!

115
00:07:13.410 --> 00:07:15.620
Here. The intel on Captain Kid.

116
00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:18.580
That's our Hongo! Always prepared!

117
00:07:18.580 --> 00:07:20.920
Shut it! Keep loading!

118
00:07:22.090 --> 00:07:24.420
So he's from the South Blue, huh?

119
00:07:24.920 --> 00:07:27.550
He's been going pretty wild...

120
00:07:31.010 --> 00:07:32.770
How many ships are there?

121
00:07:32.770 --> 00:07:34.270
Nine.

122
00:07:35.230 --> 00:07:38.230
I've seen some of these faces
on wanted posters.

123
00:07:46.780 --> 00:07:47.450
Ribbit?!

124
00:07:54.660 --> 00:07:59.210
I don't give a damn who I'm facing!

125
00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:06.800
I'll wipe 'em out in ten seconds flat!

126
00:08:07.470 --> 00:08:08.800
With this...

127
00:08:09.340 --> 00:08:11.850
Damned Punk!

128
00:08:15.020 --> 00:08:17.520
Is the ship getting pulled?!

129
00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:18.560
What is that?!

130
00:08:19.480 --> 00:08:20.810
A cannon?!

131
00:08:20.810 --> 00:08:23.110
I don't waste time with fodder!

132
00:08:23.110 --> 00:08:25.570
To anyone...

133
00:08:25.570 --> 00:08:28.570
who stands in our way...

134
00:08:39.330 --> 00:08:41.040
Get blown to hell!

135
00:09:11.610 --> 00:09:13.700
Show yourself!

136
00:09:13.700 --> 00:09:16.700
Red Hair!

137
00:09:17.950 --> 00:09:18.750
Shit!

138
00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.750
Tell the fleet to spread out!

139
00:09:22.290 --> 00:09:23.330
What's wrong, Chief?!

140
00:09:23.790 --> 00:09:25.800
Dorry! Brogy! Get ready!

141
00:09:25.800 --> 00:09:28.010
– Alright!
– Alright!

142
00:09:29.630 --> 00:09:31.630
Hard to port!

143
00:09:37.350 --> 00:09:39.310
There'll be too much damage...

144
00:09:47.320 --> 00:09:49.900
Guess he saw a pretty nasty future.

145
00:09:57.540 --> 00:10:00.660
Get blown to hell!

146
00:10:01.870 --> 00:10:03.500
Just as I thought.

147
00:10:19.060 --> 00:10:20.430
Red Hair!

148
00:10:23.940 --> 00:10:25.150
Divine Departure.

149
00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:29.080
Boss!

150
00:11:29.500 --> 00:11:30.710
He's not moving!

151
00:11:31.460 --> 00:11:32.710
He's gonna die!

152
00:11:32.710 --> 00:11:33.550
Dammit!

153
00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:35.930
Killer got hurt covering him, too!

154
00:11:45.390 --> 00:11:47.310
We surrender, Red Hair!

155
00:11:47.310 --> 00:11:48.310
Please help us!

156
00:11:48.310 --> 00:11:51.020
Don't kill our boss!

157
00:11:54.690 --> 00:11:56.700
Hey, Emma, bring them here!

158
00:11:56.700 --> 00:11:57.400
What?

159
00:11:57.400 --> 00:11:58.320
Hurry up!

160
00:12:02.280 --> 00:12:04.700
Th-These are our lode poneglyphs!

161
00:12:04.700 --> 00:12:06.000
This is all we got!

162
00:12:06.330 --> 00:12:08.710
Please spare our lives!

163
00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:24.720
Chief! This way!

164
00:12:39.820 --> 00:12:40.860
H-Hey...

165
00:12:41.370 --> 00:12:42.450
Look at the island!

166
00:12:49.870 --> 00:12:51.080
Something really bad...

167
00:12:52.330 --> 00:12:53.420
is coming!

168
00:13:05.890 --> 00:13:07.850
Hey, puny humans!

169
00:13:07.850 --> 00:13:11.020
If you point a cannon at
someone else's home...

170
00:13:13.610 --> 00:13:17.070
...don't be surprised when they fire back!

171
00:13:22.360 --> 00:13:23.950
Dominion!

172
00:14:00.400 --> 00:14:03.450
At Elbaph, in the New World...

173
00:14:05.910 --> 00:14:08.660
the Kid Pirates, led by Eustass "Captain" Kid...

174
00:14:10.910 --> 00:14:15.250
a man with a bounty of three billion berries...

175
00:14:15.920 --> 00:14:17.340
were destroyed.
